<% content_for :title do %>
  <%= title %>
<% end %>

<% content_for :stylesheet do %>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag "style" -%>
<% end %>

<% content_for :welcome do %>
    <%= do_welcome %>
<% end %>


<h2>Select Desired Half-Hourly Climate and Soil Data</h2>
<form name="select" METHOD="POST" ACTION="http://www.soils.wisc.edu/asigServlets/AWSDownload">
  <input type="hidden" name="rpt_type" value="403"/>
<B>First,</B> please select the station whose data you wish to download:
<P> The list box
below lists the stations available, showing the station number, the first
day of data available for that station, the last day of data available,
and the station's name.
<P>
<%= render :partial => 'date_selector' %>

<P><HR><P>

<B>Next, </b>please choose the data fields you wish to include:
<P>
<input TYPE="checkbox" NAME="show_first_line" VALUE="yes" CHECKED>&nbsp&nbsp Display
data field abbreviations as first line of data (column headings)
<br><input TYPE="checkbox" NAME="year_doy" VALUE="yes">&nbsp&nbsp Display date as
year and day-of-year (default is year-month-day)
<P>
<table BORDER=5 CELLPADDING=3>
<tr>
<td><input TYPE="checkbox" NAME="data_field" VALUE="stnid" CHECKED>&nbsp&nbsp Station Number</td>

<td><input TYPE="checkbox" NAME="data_field" VALUE="theDate" CHECKED>&nbsp&nbsp Date</td>

<td><input TYPE="checkbox" NAME="data_field" VALUE="theTime" CHECKED>&nbsp&nbsp Time</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td><input TYPE="checkbox" NAME="data_field" VALUE="HToPcpn" CHECKED>&nbsp&nbsp Total Precipitation
(mm)</td>

<td><input TYPE="checkbox" NAME="data_field" VALUE="HAvSol" CHECKED>&nbsp&nbsp Average Solar
Radiation (W/m2)</td>

<td><input TYPE="checkbox" NAME="data_field" VALUE="HAvTAir" CHECKED>&nbsp&nbsp Average Air
Temperature (Deg C)</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td><input TYPE="checkbox" NAME="data_field" VALUE="HAvRHum" CHECKED>&nbsp&nbsp Average Relative
Humidity (Percent)</td>

<td><input TYPE="checkbox" NAME="data_field" VALUE="HAvTS05" CHECKED>&nbsp&nbsp Average 2
Inch Soil Temperature (Deg C)</td>

<td><input TYPE="checkbox" NAME="data_field" VALUE="HAvTS10" CHECKED>&nbsp&nbsp Average 4
Inch Soil Temperature (Deg C)</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td><input TYPE="checkbox" NAME="data_field" VALUE="HAvTS50" CHECKED>&nbsp&nbsp Average 20
Inch Soil Temperature (Deg C)</td>

<td><input TYPE="checkbox" NAME="data_field" VALUE="HPkWind" CHECKED>&nbsp&nbsp Peak Wind
(m/s)</td>

<td><input TYPE="checkbox" NAME="data_field" VALUE="HAvWind" CHECKED>&nbsp&nbsp Average Wind
(m/s)</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td><input TYPE="checkbox" NAME="data_field" VALUE="HRsWind" CHECKED>&nbsp&nbsp Resultant
Wind (m/s)</td>

<td><input TYPE="checkbox" NAME="data_field" VALUE="HRsDir" CHECKED>&nbsp&nbsp Resultant Wind
Direction (Degrees)</td>

<td><input TYPE="checkbox" NAME="data_field" VALUE="HDvDir" CHECKED>&nbsp&nbsp Std. Dev. of
Res. Wind Dir. (Degrees)</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td><input TYPE="checkbox" NAME="data_field" VALUE="HAvPAR" CHECKED>&nbsp&nbsp Average P.A.R.
Radiation (uMoles/(m2s))</td>

<td><input TYPE="checkbox" NAME="data_field" VALUE="HMxWnd1" CHECKED>&nbsp&nbsp Maximum One
Minute Wind Speed (m/s)</td>

<td><input TYPE="checkbox" NAME="data_field" VALUE="HAvTDew" CHECKED>&nbsp&nbsp Average Dew
Temperature (Deg C)</td>
</tr>
</table>

<P><HR><P>

<B>Next, </b>select the date range you want:
<%= date_selector_section %>

<P><HR><P>
<B>Finally,</B> click the "Download Data" button to obtain your data: 
When the data appear in your browser window, you can copy and paste them into
a file, or use the "Save As.." function of your browser to save them. Press
the "Clear All Checkboxes" button to un-check all the data-selection boxes.
<p><input type="submit" value="Download Data">&nbsp&nbsp <input type="reset" value="Clear All Checkboxes">
</form>